Work_Description:
Scope of work is limited to;
Occupancy of an existing commercial suite, located on the 1st storey, in an existing mixed use building, name of the new business is 'Venus Envy' (relocating to a new commercial suite).

Note: this occupancy permit does not authorize any new construction, such as structural alterations or alterations to the fire suppressions systems.

Scope of work is limited to;
Demolition of Old Black Point School as per RFT 23-150
Note: Expiry date of Demo permit coincides with expiry date of submitted insurance policy 23/05/2023

Scope of work is;
Occupancy an existing commercial suite for a business known as 'Eastern Tea Bar'.  Location is a portion of a 2nd floor level of a 2 storey building.

Occupancy is subject to an on-site inspection by HRM.

Scope of work is limited to;
Relocating our existing business to 181 Damascus Road, Unit 4B with the leaseholds completed by the Landlord.  Business name is: FloorsEtc Inc.

Note: Occupancy permit is subject to an on-site inspection by HRM inspector, provide access to the suite prior to occupancy.

Tenant will use the Premises for the business of the retail sale of Steve Madden brand merchandise. 
Tenant’s Work shall include the following work:
- Refinish the existing storefront bulkhead;
- Installation of trade name sign on the storefront bulkhead;
- New interior paint job, Installation of new shelving, cabinetry, leaseholds, and fixtures;
- repair or replace any of the existing storefront glazing/flooring/back of house/existing finishes

Demolition of 155 Main St Dartmouth 

Permit Conditions;
1.) In accordance with Part 8 of the Code, Article 8.2.1.3. the entire demolition site shall include a 1.8m height construction safety fence, to restrict unauthorized access at all times.

Tenant will use the Premises solely for the business of the retail sale of Steve Madden brand merchandise.
Tenant work shall include the following:
- Refinish the existing storefront bulkhead;
- Installation of trade name sign on the storefront bulkhead;
- New interior paint job, Installation of new shelving, cabinetry, leaseholds, fixtures, and new lighting;
- repair or replace any of the existing storefront glazing/flooring/back of house/existing finishes and return them to a first-class manner.
